DevOps Tools :--
0. Plan : Jira and Open Project.
1. Source Code Management :- GIT
2. Central Repository for source code:- Github, bitbucket,Gitea
3. Build Tool:- Maven, Gradlew
4. Static Code analysis : SonarQube
5. CICD:- Jenkins,Bamboo and other cloud Services
6. Containerization:- Docker 
7. Container Orchestration/Management:- Kubernetes
8. Monitoring: Prometheus, Grafana and alertmanager
9. Data streaming:- Kafka
10. Logs Monitoring:- ELK(Elastic Search, Logstash and kibana) 

AWS Cloud Services

1.IAM : groups,users,roles and policies
2.VPC: vpc,subnets.routes,security groups, internet gateway,Nat Gateway,NACL,VPC Peering,VPC endpoints.
3.EC2:- instances, instances types,instance classes and pricing,AMI,Elastic ip,volumes,snapshots,loadbalancer, target groups,Autoscaling
4.S3:- Bucket, bucket classes and pricing,bucket policy,static web hosting.
5.RDS: infrastructure provisioning, database basics, snapshots
6.ECR: Repositories, LifeCycle Policies
7.EFS: Infrastructure Provisioning
8.Route53: DNS service, Hosted Zones, dns records
9.CloudFront :  infrastructure and demo
10.Cloud Trail: Create events and check logs
11.EKS:- infrastructure provisioning demo.


